StringValues.16: A letter of introduction, addressed to Jilsaya bint Dah in al-Arqas from Nurbaha bint Dah in the West Outpost.
StringValues.15: A letter of introduction, addressed to Jilsaya bint Dah from Nurbaha bint Dah.

Pages.Text:
Jilsaya,

This adventurer was able to recover one of mother's knives.  You should ask for help acquiring that drink you like so much.
